hail docker test environment

https://github.com/hail-is/hail

Currently builds off latest master from hail

Examples:

   $ docker run -it hail
   $ root@aa43254a73ef:/# hail -h
   ...
   $ docker run -v $PWD:/usr/work -w /usr/work -it  hail importvcf src/test/resources/sample.vcf write -o ~/sample.vds
   ...
